com.simplifier - package com.simplifier
 
com.simplifier.pre_processing - package com.simplifier.pre_processing
Provides the classes necessary to prepare the log for simplification.
com.simplifier.rules.navigation - package com.simplifier.rules.navigation
Provides the classes necessary to simplify navigation actions of the log.
com.simplifier.rules.read - package com.simplifier.rules.read
Provides the classes necessary to simplify read actions of the log.
com.simplifier.rules.write - package com.simplifier.rules.write
Provides the classes necessary to simplify write actions of the log.
com.simplifier.validation - package com.simplifier.validation
 
containsRedundantClickTextField(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.navigation.NavigationSimplifier
This method is used to check if the log contains a pattern that matches NavigationSimplifier.redundantClickTextFieldRegex, i.e the log contains "clickTextField" actions.
containsRedundantCopy(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.read.ReadSimplifier
This method is used to check if the log contains a pattern that matches ReadSimplifier.redundantFirstCopyRegex, i.e the log contains two "copy" actions, and there is any number of action between them except "paste" action.
containsRedundantDoubleEditField(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches redundantDoubleEditFieldRegex, i.e the log contains two "editField" actions and the second "editField" action has the same target name as the first "editField" action.
containsRedundantDoublePaste(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches redundantDoublePasteRegex, i.e the log contains two "paste" actions with the same target name and target value and there is any number of action between them except "copy" action with the same target name.
containsRedundantEditCell(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches redundantEditCellRegex, i.e the log contains two "editCell" actions with the same cell address, and there is any number of action between them except "getCell" action and "copyCell" action with the same cell address.
containsRedundantEditField(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches pasteEditFieldWithoutCopyRegex and does not contain a pattern that matches pasteBetweenEditFieldsRegex.
containsRedundantPasteIntoCell(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches redundantPasteIntoCellRegex, i.e the log contains two "pasteIntoCell" actions with the same workbook name, sheet name and target id (cell address) and there is any number of action between them except "copyCell" action with the same workbook name, sheet name and cell address.
containsRedundantPasteIntoRange(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.write.WriteSimplifier
Checks if the log contains a pattern that matches redundantPasteIntoRangeRegex, i.e the log contains two "pasteIntoRange" actions with the same workbook name, sheet name and target id (cell range) and there is any number of action between them except "copyRange" action with the same workbook name, sheet name and cell range.
containsSingleCopy(String) - Static method in class com.simplifier.rules.read.ReadSimplifier
This method is used to check if the log contains a pattern that matches ReadSimplifier.singleCopyRegex, i.e the log contains a single "copy" action and there is no "paste" action after it.
